Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在严肃和睿智的人生中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要和宝贵的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有桥牌  高尔夫...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成
