Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.21,1:38:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是如此快乐
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.71,1:38:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.41,1:38:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从心底出发
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.21,1:38:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往那个地方
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.15,1:38:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们会觉得这是一顶帽子  但它不是
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.99,1:39:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.91,1:39:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去一个安静的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.61,1:39:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.41,1:39:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没跟上的话
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.41,1:39:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.31,1:39:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到猫头鹰巢这里
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.81,1:39:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.31,1:39:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就快到了或还没有
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.81,1:39:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.71,1:39:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去一个安逸放松的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.91,1:39:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.81,1:39:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于到了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.61,1:39:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.81,1:39:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,度过美好的时光
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.41,1:39:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们终于敢张开双臂去拥抱
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.41,1:39:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切烦恼都消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.61,1:39:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路时
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.51,1:39:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是如此的快乐
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.51,1:39:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这些
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.71,1:39:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都不认得的记得
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.21,1:39:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发呆时
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.81,1:39:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是如此的快乐
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.91,1:39:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人世间如此美丽
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.91,1:40:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.71,1:40:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.51,1:40:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.21,1:40:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可真像
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.41,1:40:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.41,1:40:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如我是你
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.21,1:40:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.21,1:40:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把衣服弄脏了
